{"tid":94503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬英九：我的母語是湖南話 在家一直說湖南話","createTime":"2017-01-25T09:09:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-25T15:39:25.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de3d37f1cff39ad4bffd517dd0a6a2d4013bf8c4","tid":94503,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:09:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8zSVqXVKDV4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8zSVqXVKDV4&d=QfCtq%2FJ5M8ChdtAMCkZiHWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=d4ee1886\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8zSVqXVKDV4</a> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/1951340\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F1951340&d=QfCtq%2FJ5M8ChdtAMCkZiHWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=c3c5850e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F1951340&h=1da6a505\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/1951340</a> <br />\n<br />\n〔記者鄭鴻達／台北報導〕前總統馬英九今出席中華湖湘文化發展協會會員大會，暢談近代湖南名將戰史。而中國將8年對日抗戰改為14年，馬強調「台灣人不但抗日，還比大陸早42年」，指抗日應從1895年乙未戰爭算起。接著馬英九有感而發表示「清朝高層很多昏庸之輩，但中層有很多能為國民做事的官員」。<br />\n馬英九出席中華湖湘文化發展協會會員大會，因與會者主要來自中國湖南省，<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>馬先以一連串湖南話與在場者問好，並強調湖南話為其母語後</strong></span></ins>   ，隨即暢談湖南出身的中國清代、民國時期名將孫開華及劉放吾，如何在清法戰爭、中日戰爭中，智勇雙全地擊退外敵。<br />\n在說完湖南名將戰史後，馬英九談清末時局似乎有感而發，表示「看當時歷史很感慨」，「當時清朝高層是有很多昏庸之輩」，但「中層還是有很多不錯的官員，能為國為民做很多事」，並以台灣清領時期首任巡撫劉銘傳建設台灣、孫開華奠定滬尾之役戰果等。<br />\n中國教育部近日將對日抗戰起始改為「九一八事變」，使「八年抗日」拉長為14年，有意爭奪國、共對日抗戰歷史話語權，對此，馬英九表示「台灣竟有人說台灣人從不抗日」，強調應從1895年日軍登台的乙未戰爭算起，「台灣不但抗日，而且還比大陸早42年」，「要提九一八就不能不提乙未戰爭」。"},{"pid":"9e7e964bf26e1a097a498ae2e1a282ffcb637f2a","tid":94503,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:33:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d36bdc1172e26e832d3bc2c7b5b81a1f69d34d","tid":94503,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:35:13.000Z","msg":"湖南 男盜女娼"},{"pid":"816c84ebedf1aad542afb4b51a47f6145253833e","tid":94503,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:38:57.000Z","msg":"我地湖南人呢就唔衰得既"},{"pid":"4242f0aa7f64b2d7f70dd270b7ba46c3c54420c4","tid":94503,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:39:01.000Z","msg":"湖南專出狗賊"},{"pid":"5afc4558b6c931b8b8d9a8bc99642d94c0f0331a","tid":94503,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:42:21.000Z","msg":"乜撚野湖南話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 常德話同長沙話都已經差好撚遠"},{"pid":"cd4a0102a67f80b9a21fc10b52ab672f7081aeb5","tid":94503,"uid":23832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:43:31.000Z","msg":"條撚屌之前又自認客家人<br />\n依家又變身湖南幫<br />\n百變星君<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"587507fab4c3f0e6f8b81ba56164a646facf9d06","tid":94503,"uid":35914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:43:32.000Z","msg":"點奶都分唔到一官半職架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"006adad26a30d6ca54d70439ea46c73f3ab2e9b4","tid":94503,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:49:55.000Z","msg":"返支那啦"},{"pid":"5b146ccd117583e18530cf28b28ad0720500e440","tid":94503,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T10:06:32.000Z","msg":"國民黨為何在台強推國語(胡化北京話)消滅台語"},{"pid":"91ece2524f0838441fa8ec20d8ddae77d3b253f5","tid":94503,"uid":63543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T10:42:32.000Z","msg":"馬特應該出來講多啲野，曲線支持菜英文既民望<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a78c97ed5cfc834d3ad52ecb6e10edd54da4def","tid":94503,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"